Riders of Max and Gokada riders have protested the ban on operation of commercial motorcycles  in 15 local government areas of Lagos. The ban takes effect from February 1, 2020. Dissatisfied with the policy, the protest, which started from Kudirat Abiola way, Oregun, attracted hundreds of riders. They lamented the policy will affect their commerical lives and activities. They marched to the Secretariat Alausa before security operatives barricaded the entrance to the Assembly. Details shortly… T